query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(acc q1 s t1 u1 tq1) NoHashJoin(acc q1 s t1 tq1 u1 a1) NoHashJoin(a1 acc q1 s t1 tq1 u1 b) */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from so_user AS u1
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id AND u1.downvotes >= 10 AND u1.downvotes <= 100000
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('askubuntu',
'math')
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.name IN ('expectation',
'fourier-analysis',
'indefinite-integrals',
'lebesgue-integral',
'metric-spaces',
'nvidia',
'puzzle',
'software-center',
'systems-of-equations')
inner join question AS q1
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND q1.view_count >= 100 AND q1.view_count <= 100000
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND q1.id = tq1.question_id
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name IN ('Cleanup',
'Deputy',
'Disciplined',
'Fanatic',
'Great Answer',
'Inquisitive',
'Investor',
'Peer Pressure',
'Promoter',
'Self-Learner',
'Strunk & White',
'Talkative') group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
